38 SECTION 5. (1) The Water Resources Department shall promote and facilitate enrollment
39 in the federal Conservation Reserve Enhancement Program (132 Stat. 4534, 16 U.S.C. 3831a)
40 for water users in this state who voluntarily cancel ground water rights in areas where the
41 department is not allowing new rights to use ground water for irrigation.
42 (2) To carry out the provisions of subsection (1) of this section, the department may en-
43 ter into grant agreements and contracts and issue direct payments to program enrollees.
